  "text": "that it encodes visual face representations. Higher-level semantic information [CITATION_1] or even a variety of unrelated task/stimulus properties may be responsible for pattern discrimination [CITATION_2] . The latter possibility is a source of concern especially given certain limitations of the fMRI signal in decoding facial identity [CITATION_3] .",
